{"tid":1921212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢直飛香港航班4月1日開放預訂，多間航空公司機票已售罄！！","createTime":"2020-03-12T01:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T17:25:33.000Z","uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4d78cad8ac0a7536f9ab188bee0b970315feba48","tid":1921212,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:14:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://businessfocus.io/article/132684/新冠肺炎-武漢直飛香港航班4月1日開放預訂-多間航空公司部份機票已售罄\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.io%2Farticle%2F132684%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E7%9B%B4%E9%A3%9B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD4%E6%9C%881%E6%97%A5%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%82-%E5%A4%9A%E9%96%93%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E9%83%A8%E4%BB%BD%E6%A9%9F%E7%A5%A8%E5%B7%B2%E5%94%AE%E7%BD%84&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9ldOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=5545810c\" target=\"_blank\">https://businessfocus.io/article/132684/新冠肺炎-武漢直飛香港航班4月1日開放預訂-多間航空公司部份機票已售罄</a><br />\n<br />\n播毒大軍全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039890bfc28e67cd4ece5ca46e5cb9e64adbb1c2","tid":1921212,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:17:56.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200310/s00004/aff09c73dd982da07d6f1ac0e68d5cce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200310%2Fs00004%2Faff09c73dd982da07d6f1ac0e68d5cce.jpg&h=11e771e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200310/s00004/afef5521b1d2938a28a1197af93b7334.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200310%2Fs00004%2Fafef5521b1d2938a28a1197af93b7334.jpg&h=5b44aa22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22a6505e35592b7555876318391dce80976e4065","tid":1921212,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:18:18.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎（COVID-19）疫情持續爆發，多個國家及地區採取「封城」政策，而內地疫情最嚴重的武漢市自1月23日起實行封城管理，至今仍未解除。不過，攜程、途牛、航旅縱橫等內地多間網上訂票平台上，出現了自3月29日起武漢直飛上海、大連、濟南、廈門等內地多地的航班資訊。4月1日起亦有直飛香港的航班，由國泰港龍航空承運（中國國航代碼共享）。<br />\n<br />\n有傳媒查詢內地攜程網時發現，截至昨日下午5時，4月4日以前武漢直飛上海的航班已售罄。網頁圖片顯示，3月29日由武漢直飛上海的航班，涵蓋從早到晚多個時段，價格為1890至2280港元不等，涉及中國東方航空及旗下上海航空。<br />\n<br />\n武漢飛往香港航班3月29日起解禁？<br />\n<br />\n小編較早前在Skyscanner 網站上發現，從3月29日起已經可以購買從武漢離境前往香港的航班，最早的一班機為當日早上7時45分，最遲的一班則為晚上9時55分，當中所有航班同樣需要於其他地點轉機才可到達香港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://businessfocus.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/88273876_187306346020314_1237446005725593600_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.imgix.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F88273876_187306346020314_1237446005725593600_n.jpg&h=2c8ee1de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果想從武漢直飛香港，4月1日起亦有直飛香港的航班，由國泰港龍航空承運，中國國際航空代碼共享，當日售價3000元左右起。國泰航空官網強調，本年度3月9日至4月20日發出的新機票，截止到翌年2月，都可免費無限次更改。<br />\n<br />\n不過，武漢飛往澳門、台灣及海外其他城市，就暫未有直航航班提供，但旅客亦可購買轉機航程。"},{"pid":"69a65aaca5d98035f8ca80ff8f5e05e19edbbdfa","tid":1921212,"uid":69891,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:19:04.000Z","msg":"又old fake news"},{"pid":"7609f17c8cbe2b38b104794011c19c6150b85e31","tid":1921212,"uid":33441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:19:08.000Z","msg":"機場淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbf1fde50313c8e584b73ebce627f8cdfea3c58","tid":1921212,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime